text.tspan: Goals & Needs
Everyday Activities
Motivations
Ervin is big on tattoos and wants the ability to
express himself through his artwork (tattoos
included).
Due to his strict schedule, Ervin needs a convenient
way to research on the fly.
He works in an industry that is dependent on
human connection, so he needs to feel some type
of connection between himself and his artist.
Ervin travels around the world, and he needs the
ability to find local shops and artists.
Tries to squeeze an hour workout in every
morning M-F
Meets with his clients two/three days out of the
week
Ervin meets with industry friends for social
outings(dinners, bars, concerts) as often as
possible.
Is in an airport at least 2 times out of the week,
depending on his workload.
Ervin is motivated by his surroundings and
through the connections he makes.
He views everything as a form of art and seeks
inspiration on a daily basis.
He is a huge music buff and has many friends &
acquaintances in the creative industry. He is a
lover of the arts which adds to his slight
obsession of tattoos.
Frustrations
Ervins Direct Quotes
Ervin hates not making connections with his
artist. He loves building genuine connections. He
feels that a true connection helps fuel creativity.
He does not like feeling like his time is wasted. He
feels like if he books an appointment, then his
artist should be ready at the scheduled time.
“ I am a tattoo addict! As a photographer I love
expressing myself through my work and my ink is
no different. Everything is ART! ”
“ Tatts hurt so good! ”
“ I lost count after my 20th tattoo. The more the
merrier! ”
Device & Internet Usage
Ervin Green
“ The Keen Eye”
Ervin is a 32-year-old freelance
photographer, currently living in
Washington, D.C.
As a traveling photographer Ervin is
constantly on the go. He has a keen eye
for artistry and loves researching new
tattoo artists in the areas he travels to.
For convenience, he leans on his mobile
device a lot, but in a perfect world, he
would prefer to work and research solely
from his laptop.
Ervin is a social butterfly. He prides
himself on meeting new people and
making strong connections.
